THALES ENACTMENT

Deploying the Airport choreography (WP6) without using the Enactment Engine.

The airport choreography and the Enactment engine are devloped in the contexto of the CHOReOS project.

Leonardo Leite




HOWTO

For each target VM:
  1) login on the target VM
  2) sudo apt-get install git
  3) checkout thales_enactment
  4) install_chef.sh
  5) cp -R thales_enactment/chef-solo/cookbooks/* chef-solo/cookbooks
  6) edit solo.rb 
  7) edit node.json *
  8) run chef-solo
9) edit the bind_service.sh, provinding the services IPs.
10) run bind_service.sh


